{"tid":1669194,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔已經對加泰集會發出反對通知書","createTime":"2019-10-22T11:49:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T00:09:31.000Z","uid":293326,"like":41,"dislike":57,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"2e5dd9535eb889d7a7ac401c402abfff07147d6b","tid":1669194,"uid":293326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T11:49:21.000Z","msg":"我屌哂你班冷氣軍師/風向撚<br />\n加泰獨立我無意見<br />\n但加泰手足同樣面對緊黑警不合理暴力及政治審判<br />\n點解唔可以connect?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講到集會好撚大件事<br />\n又影響美帝乜乜柒柒<br />\n美帝先唔會咁撚幼稚<br />\n因為區區一個集會唔理利益而割香港<br />\n星期四一撚定去<br />\n我要證明比你地班冷氣風向撚睇<br />\n乜撚野影響國際主流意見<br />\n乜撚野美帝會唔鐘意<br />\n全部都係廢話<br />\n最後香港局勢根本無變<br />\n反而意外地connect 到同樣醞釀緊抗爭既地方<br />\n成日因為所謂美帝觀感，畫面唔好睇<br />\n就斬自己腳指，一係休息<br />\n覺唔覺得自己好撚肉酸<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VoJXM16.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVoJXM16.png&h=d7ec520d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bf9cce4c019fa544b85dd0e75253a65f9a0e5ecd","tid":1669194,"uid":293326,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T11:52:25.000Z","msg":"Btw 香港人集會唔需要黑警不反對通知書<br />\n同樣唔需要連登仔既所謂反對<br />\n集會目的由頭到尾唔係講緊支持加泰獨立<br />\n只係講警暴及政治犯問題<br />\n邊個話去集會就係支持加泰獨立既都係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba6751a582b9fc6c8c784d9860e245a5a89bddc2","tid":1669194,"uid":293326,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T12:08:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同樣面對警暴同政治打壓就要connect"},{"pid":"7e8f0723ecd021b5438a9319615a88ec586c0b9f","tid":1669194,"uid":114186,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T17:04:14.000Z","msg":"已經有傻西騎劫緊 如果影響到香港你地點負責?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AdJEhKn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-sr