住，每次有集會都有人俾人拉，每次其實人數都有減少到，咪再做d吃力唔討好嘅on9。有時間落區追擊下民賤聯，裝修下唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbc484502573ab840d41e1fe3ffdf1bf67b27eb1","tid":1669194,"uid":78947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T19:00:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"481492e35bdcbe4f47cc27b279027f05fa1eecae","tid":1669194,"uid":283668,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T19:07:38.000Z","msg":"手足獨立思考，各人自己決定<br />\n<br />\n問個個叫Bosco <br />\nSir I am kinda stuck. Do you think HKers&rsquo; stance on catalonia matters with respect to HK gaining support from the US and other international countries? There is a hot debate among HKers now. Any insight is much appreciated!<br />\n<br />\n答嘅係Solomon <br />\nGreat ?! Let other🌐movements follow🇭🇰's lead. But don't link your🇭🇰freedom movement 2 Catalonia's independence movement. Don't give ammo 2🇨🇳CCP 2 label you as a pro-independence movement. 光復香港，時代革命 is 2 restore🇭🇰autonomy through🇭🇰protests - the revolution of your times.<br />\n<br />\n本人仍然不撐，不想大家再步「臨時宣言」的後塵"},{"pid":"335951ea9cd90c6f0177e569c9608b955dc1ac4c","tid":1669194,"uid":7854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T19:09:53.000Z","msg":"不了  p牌仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6d1e9bc78c909ed94caf9c8dba31a6813473202","tid":1669194,"uid":284304,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T19:10:42.000Z","msg":"遊行舉下旗都可以話支持人地自由(其實人地根本就有自由)<br />\n反警暴(獨立革命根本警暴推高一個層次國際輿論本身就少)<br />\n而係特登搞個集會?<br />\n搞集會根本同支持人地獨立冇任何分別<br />\n你個主題係咩 根本唔係掌握你係你張海報 而係外媒點寫<br />\n根本加泰獨立呢個話題就唔適合香港插手<br />\n獨派為左打飛機將香港綁上加泰呢架烈火戰車黎R光環根本就其心可誅<br />\n叫佢搞全球抗暴主題又唔肯呢點已經心照不宣啦<br />\n即使只有1%機會比媒體抹黑 我都唔會想博<br />\n我唔會阻止你地去 但我希望你地諗清楚到底你去係支持d咩<br />\n到底你想香港贏 定加泰獨立"},{"pid":"c61acb798911077baec30dc3432a0b8e18756daf","tid":1669194,"uid":2